uch as finance, marketing, and human resources. We are committed to delivering value and driving sustainable growth for our clients.\"}]}]', '[]', '2023-06-06 10:59:17', NULL),
(9, 'Workshop: Introduction to Data Science', ' Data Academy', '2023-11-15 14:00:00', '2023-11-15 17:00:00', 'Dive into the exciting field of data science with this introductory workshop. Learn the basics of data analysis, machine learning, and data visualization techniques. Whether you\'re a beginner or looking to enhance your data skills, this workshop will provide you with valuable knowledge and hands-on experience.', '[{\"keyword\": \"workshop\", \"keywordId\": 0}, {\"keyword\": \"data science\", \"keywordId\": 1}, {\"keyword\": \"analytics\", \"keywordId\": 2}, {\"keyword\": \" machine learning\", \"keywordId\": 3}]', '[{\"id\": 8, \"name\": \"Robert Davis\", \"role\": \"Chief Technology Officer\", \"email\": \"robert.davis@example.com\", \"image\": \"https://images.pexels.com/photos/1300402/pexels-photo-1300402.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=2\", \"phone\": \"+1 555-246-8109\", \"twitter\": \"@robertdavis\", \"facebook\": \"https://www.facebook.com/robertdavis\", \"linkedin\": \"https://www.linkedin.com/in/robertdavis\", \"location\": \"789 Oak Road, City, Country\", \"created_at\": {\"date\": \"2023-06-06 10:17:05.000000\", \"timezone\": \"Europe/Helsinki\", \"timezone_type\": 3}, \"updated_at\": null, \"description\": \"Robert Davis is a technology visionary with extensive experience in driving innovation and managing complex IT projects. He specializes in leveraging cutting-edge technologies to transform businesses and enhance operational efficiency.\", \"organizations\": [{\"id\": 11, \"name\": \"QRS Industries\", \"email\": \"sales@qrsindustries.com\", \"image\": \"https://images.pexels.com/photos/716398/pexels-photo-716398.jpeg\", \"phone\": \"+1 555-789-0123\", \"address\": \"789 Oak Street, City, Country\", \"locatiion\": \"test 1\", \"created_at\": {\"date\": \"2023-06-06 09:58:15.000000\", \"timezone\": \"Europe/Helsinki\", \"timezone_type\": 3}, \"updated_at\": null, \"description\": \"QRS Industries is a renowned manufacturing comp